<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>You've Got a New Request</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; background-color:
      #f8f9fc; padding: 20px; margin: 0; } .container { background-color:
      #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,
      0, 0, 0.1); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; } .header img { max-width:
      100px; height: auto; } .content h1 { color: #1a1a33; font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 20px; } .content p { color: #373737;
      font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; } .button { display: inline-block;
      background-color: #6c6bd4; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding:
      10px 20px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; } .footer p { color:
      #373737; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 10px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="LifeBlud_Logo" />
      </div>
      <hr />
      <div class="content">
        <h1>You've Got a New Request</h1>
        <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
        <p>
          You have received a new blood donation request from
          <strong>{{organizationName}}</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Kindly log in to your account to view the details of the request and
          respond accordingly.
        </p>
        <a href="{{loginLink}}" class="button">Log in to my account</a>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact
          us.</p>
      </div>
      <hr />
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>LifeBlud Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>